:warning: PSA: mypy checks may not run correctly in your jenkins builds (see this thread (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C035SLYCJ9X/p1667245776538909))! To avoid accidentally merging broken code, please make sure to run `make test` locally before merging in any PRs that touch Python code. :snake:

This PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/32745) will fix Python typechecking in CI. I'll send another message when it is merged, at which point you should rebase off of this change to ensure your code is properly checked in CI. Thanks!
